{"snp2.7:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.7 ","snp2.7:0.2":"Brahmanadhammikasutta ","snp2.7:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp2.7:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","snp2.7:1.3":"Atha kho sambahula kosalaka brahmanamahasala jinna vuddha mahallaka addhagata vayoanuppatta yena bhagava tenupasankamimsu; upasankamitva bhagavata saddhim sammodimsu. ","snp2.7:1.4":"Sammodaniyam katham saraniyam vitisaretva ekamantam nisidimsu. Ekamantam nisinna kho te brahmanamahasala bhagavantam etadavocum: ","snp2.7:1.5":"“sandissanti nu kho, bho gotama, etarahi brahmana porananam brahmananam brahmanadhamme”ti? ","snp2.7:1.6":"“Na kho, brahmana, sandissanti etarahi brahmana porananam brahmananam brahmanadhamme”ti. ","snp2.7:1.7":"“Sadhu no bhavam gotamo porananam brahmananam brahmanadhammam bhasatu, sace bhoto gotamassa agaru”ti. ","snp2.7:1.8":"“Tena hi, brahmana, sunatha, sadhukam manasi karotha, bhasissami”ti. ","snp2.7:1.9":"“Evam, bho”ti kho te brahmanamahasala bhagavato paccassosum. ","snp2.7:1.10":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","snp2.7:2.1":"“Isayo pubbaka asum, ","snp2.7:2.2":"sannatatta tapassino; ","snp2.7:2.3":"Panca kamagune hitva, ","snp2.7:2.4":"attadatthamacarisum. ","snp2.7:3.1":"Na pasu brahmananasum, ","snp2.7:3.2":"na hirannam na dhaniyam; ","snp2.7:3.3":"Sajjhayadhanadhannasum, ","snp2.7:3.4":"brahmam nidhimapalayum. ","snp2.7:4.1":"Yam nesam pakatam asi, ","snp2.7:4.2":"dvarabhattam upatthitam; ","snp2.7:4.3":"Saddhapakatamesanam, ","snp2.7:4.4":"datave tadamannisum. ","snp2.7:5.1":"Nanarattehi vatthehi, ","snp2.7:5.2":"sayanehavasathehi ca; ","snp2.7:5.3":"Phita janapada rattha, ","snp2.7:5.4":"te namassimsu brahmane. ","snp2.7:6.1":"Avajjha brahmana asum, ","snp2.7:6.2":"ajeyya dhammarakkhita; ","snp2.7:6.3":"Na ne koci nivaresi, ","snp2.7:6.4":"kuladvaresu sabbaso. ","snp2.7:7.1":"Atthacattalisam vassani, ","snp2.7:7.2":"(komara) Brahmacariyam carimsu te; ","snp2.7:7.3":"Vijjacaranapariyetthim, ","snp2.7:7.4":"Acarum brahmana pure. ","snp2.7:8.1":"Na brahmana annamagamum, ","snp2.7:8.2":"napi bhariyam kinimsu te; ","snp2.7:8.3":"Sampiyeneva samvasam, ","snp2.7:8.4":"sangantva samarocayum. ","snp2.7:9.1":"Annatra tamha samaya, ","snp2.7:9.2":"utuveramanim pati; ","snp2.7:9.3":"Antara methunam dhammam, ","snp2.7:9.4":"nassu gacchanti brahmana. ","snp2.7:10.1":"Brahmacariyanca silanca, ","snp2.7:10.2":"ajjavam maddavam tapam; ","snp2.7:10.3":"Soraccam avihimsanca, ","snp2.7:10.4":"khantincapi avannayum. ","snp2.7:11.1":"Yo nesam paramo asi, ","snp2.7:11.2":"Brahma dalhaparakkamo; ","snp2.7:11.3":"Sa vapi methunam dhammam, ","snp2.7:11.4":"Supinantepi nagama. ","snp2.7:12.1":"Tassa vattamanusikkhanta, ","snp2.7:12.2":"Idheke vinnujatika; ","snp2.7:12.3":"Brahmacariyanca silanca, ","snp2.7:12.4":"Khantincapi avannayum. ","snp2.7:13.1":"Tandulam sayanam vattham, ","snp2.7:13.2":"Sappitelanca yaciya; ","snp2.7:13.3":"Dhammena samodhanetva, ","snp2.7:13.4":"Tato yannamakappayum. ","snp2.7:14.1":"Upatthitasmim yannasmim, ","snp2.7:14.2":"Nassu gavo hanimsu te; ","snp2.7:14.3":"Yatha mata pita bhata, ","snp2.7:14.4":"Anne vapi ca nataka; ","snp2.7:14.5":"Gavo no parama mitta, ","snp2.7:14.6":"Yasu jayanti osadha. ","snp2.7:15.1":"Annada balada ceta, ","snp2.7:15.2":"Vannada sukhada tatha; ","snp2.7:15.3":"Etamatthavasam natva, ","snp2.7:15.4":"Nassu gavo hanimsu te. ","snp2.7:16.1":"Sukhumala mahakaya, ","snp2.7:16.2":"Vannavanto yasassino; ","snp2.7:16.3":"Brahmana sehi dhammehi, ","snp2.7:16.4":"Kiccakiccesu ussuka; ","snp2.7:16.5":"Yava loke avattimsu, ","snp2.7:16.6":"Sukhamedhitthayam paja. ","snp2.7:17.1":"Tesam asi vipallaso, ","snp2.7:17.2":"Disvana anuto anum; ","snp2.7:17.3":"Rajino ca viyakaram, ","snp2.7:17.4":"Nariyo samalankata. ","snp2.7:18.1":"Rathe cajannasamyutte, ","snp2.7:18.2":"Sukate cittasibbane; ","snp2.7:18.3":"Nivesane nivese ca, ","snp2.7:18.4":"Vibhatte bhagaso mite. ","snp2.7:19.1":"Gomandalaparibyulham, ","snp2.7:19.2":"Narivaraganayutam; ","snp2.7:19.3":"Ularam manusam bhogam, ","snp2.7:19.4":"Abhijjhayimsu brahmana. ","snp2.7:20.1":"Te tattha mante ganthetva, ","snp2.7:20.2":"Okkakam tadupagamum; ","snp2.7:20.3":"Pahutadhanadhannosi, ","snp2.7:20.4":"Yajassu bahu te vittam; ","snp2.7:20.5":"Yajassu bahu te dhanam. ","snp2.7:21.1":"Tato ca raja sannatto, ","snp2.7:21.2":"Brahmanehi rathesabho; ","snp2.7:21.3":"Assamedham purisamedham, ","snp2.7:21.4":"Sammapasam vajapeyyam niraggalam; ","snp2.7:21.5":"Ete yage yajitvana, ","snp2.7:21.6":"Brahmananamada dhanam. ","snp2.7:22.1":"Gavo sayananca vatthanca, ","snp2.7:22.2":"Nariyo samalankata; ","snp2.7:22.3":"Rathe cajannasamyutte, ","snp2.7:22.4":"Sukate cittasibbane. ","snp2.7:23.1":"Nivesanani rammani, ","snp2.7:23.2":"Suvibhattani bhagaso; ","snp2.7:23.3":"Nanadhannassa puretva, ","snp2.7:23.4":"Brahmananamada dhanam. ","snp2.7:24.1":"Te ca tattha dhanam laddha, ","snp2.7:24.2":"Sannidhim samarocayum; ","snp2.7:24.3":"Tesam icchavatinnanam, ","snp2.7:24.4":"Bhiyyo tanha pavaddhatha; ","snp2.7:24.5":"Te tattha mante ganthetva, ","snp2.7:24.6":"Okkakam puna mupagamum. ","snp2.7:25.1":"Yatha apo ca pathavi ca, ","snp2.7:25.2":"Hirannam dhanadhaniyam; ","snp2.7:25.3":"Evam gavo manussanam, ","snp2.7:25.4":"Parikkharo so hi paninam; ","snp2.7:25.5":"Yajassu bahu te vittam, ","snp2.7:25.6":"Yajassu bahu te dhanam. ","snp2.7:26.1":"Tato ca raja sannatto, ","snp2.7:26.2":"Brahmanehi rathesabho; ","snp2.7:26.3":"Neka satasahassiyo, ","snp2.7:26.4":"Gavo yanne aghatayi. ","snp2.7:27.1":"Na pada na visanena, ","snp2.7:27.2":"Nassu himsanti kenaci; ","snp2.7:27.3":"Gavo elakasamana, ","snp2.7:27.4":"Sorata kumbhaduhana; ","snp2.7:27.5":"Ta visane gahetvana, ","snp2.7:27.6":"Raja satthena ghatayi. ","snp2.7:28.1":"Tato deva pitaro ca, ","snp2.7:28.2":"Indo asurarakkhasa; ","snp2.7:28.3":"Adhammo iti pakkandum, ","snp2.7:28.4":"Yam sattham nipati gave. ","snp2.7:29.1":"Tayo roga pure asum, ","snp2.7:29.2":"Iccha anasanam jara; ","snp2.7:29.3":"Pasunanca samarambha, ","snp2.7:29.4":"Atthanavutimagamum. ","snp2.7:30.1":"Eso adhammo dandanam, ","snp2.7:30.2":"Okkanto purano ahu; ","snp2.7:30.3":"Adusikayo hannanti, ","snp2.7:30.4":"Dhamma dhamsanti yajaka. ","snp2.7:31.1":"Evameso anudhammo, ","snp2.7:31.2":"Porano vinnugarahito; ","snp2.7:31.3":"Yattha edisakam passati, ","snp2.7:31.4":"Yajakam garahati jano. ","snp2.7:32.1":"Evam dhamme viyapanne, ","snp2.7:32.2":"Vibhinna suddavessika; ","snp2.7:32.3":"Puthu vibhinna khattiya, ","snp2.7:32.4":"Patim bhariyavamannatha. ","snp2.7:33.1":"Khattiya brahmabandhu ca, ","snp2.7:33.2":"Ye canne gottarakkhita; ","snp2.7:33.3":"Jativadam nirakatva, ","snp2.7:33.4":"Kamanam vasamanvagun”ti. ","snp2.7:34.1":"Evam vutte, te brahmanamahasala bhagavantam etadavocum: ","snp2.7:34.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama …pe… ","snp2.7:34.3":"upasake no bhavam gotamo dharetu ajjatagge panupete saranam gate”ti. ","snp2.7:34.4":"Brahmanadhammikasuttam sattamam. "}